gomodel:SYNGO_2222  a     owl:Ontology ;
        rdfs:comment      "Automated change 2024-03-14: GO:0099061 replaced by GO:0098839" , "Rationale: LRRC7/Densin-180 was enriched in postsynaptic density fractions.\n\n16/01/2018 Pim\n- Fig.8: \"Immunocytochemical localization of densin-180 at synapses in dissociated hippocampal neurons\"\nThis figure shows that LRRC7; Densin-180 is co-localized with PSD-95 and Synapsin-I.\n- Based on the known transmembrane topology of the protein, the \"integral component of ... membrane\" term was chosen.. Experimental description: MATERIALS AND METHODS\nSubcellular fractions of rat brain\nForebrain homogenates, synaptosomes, and detergent-extracted PSD fractions were prepared from Sprague Dawley rats." ;
        lego:modelstate   "production" ;
        dc:contributor    "https://orcid.org/0000-0001-5518-6584" , "https://orcid.org/0000-0001-6194-9648" ;
        dc:date           "2024-03-14" ;
        dc:title          "SYNGO_CC_2222" ;
        pav:providedBy    "https://syngo.vu.nl" ;
        biolink:in_taxon  "http://purl.obolibrary.org/obo/NCBITaxon_10116" .

